 and we would have to construct a distribution 
\begin_inset Formula $p$
\end_inset

 to model this.
 We shall define 
\begin_inset Formula $p$
\end_inset

 over 3 binary variables 
\begin_inset Formula $X,Y,Z$
\end_inset

 as follows: 
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
