\begin_inset Formula $p$
\end_inset

 satisfies 
\begin_inset Formula $\mathcal{I}_{LM}(\mathcal{H})$
\end_inset

 and not 
\begin_inset Formula $\mathcal{I}(\mathcal{H})$
\end_inset

.
